Replaces: led-ugreen-dkms
Description: UGREEN DXP LED kernel module (DKMS)
 A reverse-engineered LED kernel module for UGREEN DXP NAS devices.
 This package contains the kernel module source with DKMS support for
 automatic rebuilding when the kernel is updated.
 .
 The module provides sysfs interface for LED control and integrates
 with the kernel LED subsystem, supporting triggers like netdev and oneshot.
